ok. go to the south -west corner of your area, and type the replace the 1st lot of XXXX with the coords, go to the north-east corner of your area adn type the 2nd XXXX coord.
then go back to the south-west corner and type the 1st YYYY coord, then back to the north-east corner and type the 2nd YYYY coord
